comments: Harden (LAC) gathers the ball on both feet and takes two steps before shooting.
Conley (MIN) is in the paint for at or about three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Leonard (LAC) raises his left arm during the pursuit of the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Gobert's (MIN) arm as the two come together.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Edwards (MIN) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Harden (LAC) brings his off-arm outwards and marginal contact occurs with McDaniels' (MIN) arm as Harden clears space during the drive.
Harden (LAC) briefly brings his off-arm around McDaniels' (MIN) arm and marginal contact occurs with McDaniels  as the two come together during the drive.
Westbrook (LAC) steps into Gobert's (MIN) path and initiates illegal body contact with his shoulder and with his foot, affecting his FOM off-ball.
Powel (LAC) commits a take foul on Gobert (MIN).
George (LAC) commits a take foul on Edwards (MIN).
Westbrook (LAC) extends his arms and initiates contact with Gobert (MIN) that dislodges him from his rebounding position, which affects his ability to pursue the loose ball.

Westbrook (LAC) elevates and makes a natural basketball move when his left arm is brought to the side and marginal contact occurs with Gobert's (MIN) face.  Contact to an opponent's head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Gobert (MIN) jumps towards Westbrook and initiates illegal body contact which affects his driving shot attempt.
Anderson (MIN) reaches in and makes marginal contact while defending Westbrook's (LAC) drive.
